    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 37-57-104, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO AUTHORIZE THE LEVYING AUTHORITY FOR A SCHOOL DISTRICT TO APPROVE, IN FULL OR IN PART, A REQUEST FOR AN INCREASE IN THE AD VALOREM TAX EFFORT FOR THE SCHOOL DISTRICT; TO AMEND SECTION 37-57-105, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, IN CONFORMITY TO THE PROVISIONS OF THIS ACT; TO BRING FORWARD SECTION 37-57-107, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH RELATES TO THE LEVY OF AD VALOREM TAXES FOR SCHOOL DISTRICTS, FOR PURPOSES OF POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
